<article class="news-article">
    <time class="bar-time" datetime="2014-09-23">September 23, 2014</time>
    <h3>Feature focus</h3>
    <p class="doc">
    Recent changes to the catalogue include the addition of clearer indications of the class number, telling you precisely where to find the book on the shelf, better linking to e-resources, improved accessibility design, plus the option to limit a search to journal titles.  Further enhancements are planned for next month.  Thank you for the feedback received so far, which has led to these changes, and also highlighted a couple of bugs that have now been fixed.
    </p>
