<article class="news-article">
    <time class="bar-time" datetime="2013-09-30">September 30, 2013</time>
    <h3>New library catalogue search interface</h3>
    <p class="doc">
    Welcome to the Library’s new library catalogue search interface.  The new catalogue has been designed to provide a host of features and ways of finding the items you need.  Over the coming months we’ll showcase these via these announcements: you can also discover them yourself by just entering a search in the box above to get going.  The new catalogue is designed for accessibility on mobile and tablet devices as well as desktops/laptops.  Give the site a try on Android, iPhone, iPad, Windows Mobile or any other such device.
    </p>
